casebody.data:
Simon E. RODRIGUEZ, as Chapter 7 Trustee for the Bankruptcy Estate of United Western Bancorp, Inc., petitioner,
v.
FEDERAL DEPOSIT INSURANCE CORPORATION, as Receiver for United Western Bank. No. 18-1269. Supreme Court of the United States June 28, 2019.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit granted.
